README file for Courier-Authlib package for Frugalware GNU/Linux.
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Original config files provided by Courier-authlib source package
has been moved out from /etc/courier. The authdaemonrc config
file shipped with Frugalware has been setup to authenticate from
/etc/shadow. If you want to change look at:

/usr/share/doc/courier-authlib-$pkgver/examples.
 
Share and enjoy! :) 
